how can i change the way my name displays in webmail stanford answers stanford university stanford answers how can i change the way my name displays in webmail categories accounts and ids administrative applications anti virus and security computer operating systems connecting to the network desktop hardware and support email and calendar help desk restricted information on it services software at stanford stanford hospital and clinics telephones and cable tv unix systems and software web services user login login with your sunet id home how can i change the way my name displays in webmail search this site students may adjust the way their name appears in stanford webmail in two ways option 1 change the way their name appears in all university systems including their directory listing by adjusting their preferred name option 2 change their webmail personal information settings the change applies only to webmail option 1 modifying preferred name students should contact the student services center and ask to modify their preferred name in axess once the update is made by the student services center the update should appear in webmail and stanfordwho within a few hours faculty and staff can make this change via stanfordyou option 2 changing webmail settings members of the stanford community can change their webmail settings by following the instructions below log into stanford webmail click the options icon on the toolbar in general options click personal information from the your default identity drop down menu select your identity for most people this will just be default identity edit the your full name field to include your name as you would like it to appear click the save options button webmail stanford university 450 serra mall stanford california 94305 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints
